Use bold, oversized text on one side that says: "PART 1". Make the colors highly saturated with strong contrast, dramatic shadows, glowing highlights, and a polished AAA video game thumbnail style. Make it look like an official Marvel's Spider-Man 2 YouTube thumbnail with maximum click-through appeal.", "size": "1792x1008", "quality": "medium", "n": 1, "output_format": "png"}
